          password exposure from 2013 that reveals a predictable credential pattern.
          Cross-referenced against the org chart to identify financial authority.
        </div>
        <div class="session-result">→ 3 CRITICAL personnel findings · Entity graph auto-populated</div>
      </div>

      <div class="session-block animate-in stagger-3">
        <div class="session-time">08:22 – 08:55</div>
        <div class="session-title">Entity Graph + Attack Path Analysis</div>
