        </div>
        <div class="session-result">→ CFO identified as highest betweenness centrality node</div>
      </div>

      <div class="session-block animate-in stagger-4">
        <div class="session-time">08:55 – 10:15</div>
        <div class="session-title">SE Campaign Design & Staging</div>
