          to AP team exploiting DMARC vulnerability. Per-recipient tracking, credential
          capture landing page, automated redirect to reduce suspicion. Tier 2 approval
          gate enforced before deployment.
        </div>
        <div class="session-result">→ SE-001 staged and deployed at 10:15 EDT</div>
      </div>

      <div class="session-block animate-in stagger-5">
        <div class="session-time">10:24</div>
        <div class="session-title">Credential Captured</div>
        <div class="session-desc">
